    <item>
      <title>特朗普淡化中国利用 TikTok 监视美国人的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-downplays-threat-of-china-using-tiktok-to-spy-on-americans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周三在接受福克斯新闻采访时淡化了 TikTok 带来的国家安全风险。几天前，特朗普曾表示，TikTok 不会受到可能迫使其关闭的立法限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-downplays-threat-of-china-using-tiktok-to-spy-on-americans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 03:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关注运河 卢比奥计划首次出访巴拿马</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/marco-rubio-plans-to-visit-panama-as-trump-eyes-canal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士称，美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥计划最早于下周前往拉丁美洲访问巴拿马，凸显了唐纳德·特朗普总统收回巴拿马运河的认真态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/marco-rubio-plans-to-visit-panama-as-trump-eyes-canal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 02:11:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命安全部门负责人为特勤局局长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-taps-head-of-security-detail-as-secret-service-director</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统已选定肖恩·柯伦 (Sean Curran) 担任美国特勤局新任局长，后者曾是 2024 年竞选期间负责其安保工作的特工，在两次针对当时的共和党候选人的暗杀未遂后，美国特勤局受到了严格审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-taps-head-of-security-detail-as-secret-service-director</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 02:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普时代，达沃斯世界领导人纷纷表态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/one-by-one-world-leaders-in-davos-fall-in-line-in-trump-era</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他不会亲自出席，他的视频演讲将在世界经济论坛即将结束之际发布。但唐纳德·特朗普仍然是达沃斯论坛上每个人都想谈论的话题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/one-by-one-world-leaders-in-davos-fall-in-line-in-trump-era</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 01:25:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国和东南亚国家承诺打击诈骗中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/china-southeast-asian-nations-pledge-to-deal-with-scam-centers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国、泰国和其他国家已达成协议，将重点打击东南亚国家的网络犯罪中心 — — 这一迹象表明各国政府决心打击窃取人民财富并破坏旅游业的犯罪团伙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/china-southeast-asian-nations-pledge-to-deal-with-scam-centers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 01:17:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特领导人在特朗普通话中承诺投资 6000 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/saudi-leader-offers-600-billion-investment-pledge-in-trump-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据沙特国家通讯社 SPA 报道，沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼告诉总统唐纳德·特朗普，沙特愿意在未来四年内将对美投资和贸易额扩大 6000 亿美元，如果有机会，金额甚至会更多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/saudi-leader-offers-600-billion-investment-pledge-in-trump-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 01:10:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将再次将胡塞武装指定为恐怖分子，推翻拜登的立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-will-again-designate-houthis-as-terrorists-reversing-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统周三签署命令，再次将也门胡塞武装组织列为恐怖组织——近四年前拜登政府撤销了这一称号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-will-again-designate-houthis-as-terrorists-reversing-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 00:05:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥抨击中国，誓言为菲律宾提供“铁腕”防御</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/us-under-trump-says-philippines-defense-commitments-ironclad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥在任职初期与菲律宾和印尼外长讨论南海争议水域问题时，批评北京在南海采取了“危险和破坏稳定”的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/us-under-trump-says-philippines-defense-commitments-ironclad</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:32:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治危机下韩国经济艰难增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/south-korea-s-economy-struggles-for-growth-amid-political-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个季度，韩国总统尹锡烈宣布短暂戒严，消费者信心受到重创，而企业和政策制定者也开始担心唐纳德·特朗普可能征收贸易关税，韩国经济也随之持续下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/south-korea-s-economy-struggles-for-growth-amid-political-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克和奥特曼就特朗普大肆宣传的 100 亿美元人工智能项目发生争执</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/musk-says-firms-backing-trump-ai-initiative-don-t-have-the-money</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克公开质疑那些加入唐纳德·特朗普总统承诺投资数千亿美元用于人工智能基础设施建设的公司是否能够兑现承诺，这暴露了白宫内部早期的裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/musk-says-firms-backing-trump-ai-initiative-don-t-have-the-money</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:50:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
